OL,7,FA helicopter experienced a "massive
OL,8,Fjolt" shortly before it crashed,
OL,9,Fleaving a renowned racehorce owner
OL,10,Fhospitalised for several months, a
OL,11,Freport investigating the incident has
OL,12,Ffound.
OL,14,FDai Walters required treatment in
OL,15,Fintensive care after the main rotor
OL,16,Fblade of the helicopter hit nearby
OL,17,Ftrees upon take off from a landing
OL,18,Ffield near in 2022.
