OL,7,FFour other passengers, including
OL,8,Ftrainer Sam Thomas, suffered minor
OL,9,Finjuries in the incident in
OL,10,FDenbighshire.
OL,12,FThe report found at least four of the
OL,13,Ffive passengers were not wearing
OL,14,Fseatbelts, and deemed it was "likely
OL,15,Fthat, had all passengers been secured
OL,16,Fby their seat harnesses, the level of
OL,17,Finjuries sustained could have been
OL,18,Fless severe".
