OL,7,FThe Air Accidents Investigation
OL,8,FBranch's report detailed how the pilot
OL,9,Fcollected the passengers and their
OL,10,Fbelongings from a landing area in
OL,11,FLisvane, Cardiff, at 8:30am, arriving
OL,12,Fat a shooting lodge in Llanelidan by
OL,13,Fapproximately 9:20am.
OL,15,FThe return flight to Cardiff was
OL,16,Fsupposed to take off at around 4.30pm
OL,17,F- before sunset - but did not depart
OL,18,Funtil after passengers had returned
OL,19,Ffrom the shooting lodge and taken
OL,20,Ftheir seats at around 5.15pm, by which
OL,21,Ftime it was almost dark.
