OL,7,FThe landing site the helicopter took
OL,8,Foff from was unlit, but the pilot said
OL,9,Fhe felt able to leave the ground
OL,10,Fvertically and could see what he
OL,11,Fdescribed as a "vague horizon" ahead.
OL,13,FThe report detailed that the pilot was
OL,14,Fplanning to use the light from the
OL,15,Fwindows of the shooting lodge,
OL,16,FNantclwyd Lodge, as a marker as the
OL,17,Fhelicopter made its climb.
