OL,3,CHelicopter suffered 'massive jolt'
OL,4,Cbefore crash which left man in
OL,5,Cintensive care
OL,7,FHe said he felt a "massive jolt" at
OL,8,Froughly 30 or 40 feet in the air, with
OL,9,Fthe helicopter shaking violently and
OL,10,Ffalling to the ground.
OL,12,FIt was found the rotor blades had
OL,13,F"sustained catastrophic damage" after
OL,14,Fstriking nearby trees.
OL,16,FWith the helicopter coming to a stop,
OL,17,Fthe pilot unstrapped himself, stood up
OL,18,Fand opened the left cockpit door,
OL,19,Fwhich by this point was above him.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/10
