OL,7,FHe then opened the cabin door, helping
OL,8,Ffour passengers to get out.
OL,10,FHowever, the pilot found Mr Walters
OL,11,Fwas lying unconscious at the bottom of
OL,12,Fthe cabin in "significant medical
OL,13,Fdistress."
OL,15,FAfter being carried to the lodge, Mr
OL,16,FWalters was given CPR by the pilot,
OL,17,Fwho was guided by the emergency
OL,18,Fservices operator.
