OL,7,FThe report found some, if not all, of
OL,8,Fthe passengers ended up on top of the
OL,9,Fracehorse owner after the crash.
OL,11,FThe report said it was "likely that,
OL,12,Fhad all passengers been secured by
OL,13,Ftheir seat harnesses, the level of
OL,14,Finjuries sustained could have been
OL,15,Fless severe".
