OL,7,FThe pilot subsequently said he
OL,8,Fremembered seeing passengers
OL,9,F"rearranging their seatbelts" after
OL,10,Fthey sat down but did not visually
OL,11,Fconfirm they had securely fastened
OL,12,Fthem before the cabin was closed.
OL,14,FThe report found the helicopter had no
OL,15,Ftechnical issues or failures which led
OL,16,Fto the crash, although it identified
OL,17,Fnumerous issues which might have
OL,18,Fprevented the accident. These included
OL,19,F"contradictory and potentially
OL,20,Fconfusing" information about take off
OL,21,Fand landing protocols at night.
