OL,7,FThe operator of the helicopter took
OL,8,Fseveral actions following the
OL,9,Faccident, including updating its
OL,10,Foperations manual and log pages,
OL,11,Finstructing pilots to do an annual
OL,12,Fnight flying training programme and
OL,13,Fbuying deployable lighting sets to be
OL,14,Fused on flights where there might be
OL,15,Fan unexpected night take-off.
